<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="enjoyment-n">enjoyment <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪn'dʒɔɪmənt/    美 /ɪn'dʒɔɪmənt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-pleasure">1.★ <strong>享受；欢乐；乐趣 (pleasure)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He eats each mouthful with great enjoyment. 
他每一口都吃得津津有味。</p><footer>人教④ – 3</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She's not a professional. She draws for her own enjoyment.
她不是职业画家，她画画只是为了自娱自乐。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>乐事：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Children like to share interests and enjoyments with their parents. 
孩子们喜欢同父母一起分享各种兴趣和乐事。</p></div></div>